  <update_contact>139514123+sugarycandybar@users.noreply.github.com</update_contact>
  <description>
    <p>
      Hosty simplifies the process of creating and managing Minecraft servers on Linux. 
      It removes technical barriers by automating the installation of necessary server 
      files and handling the required Java runtimes for you.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Built-in Modrinth browser for easy discovery and mod installation</li>
      <li>Integrated Playit support for hosting without manual port forwarding</li>
      <li>Graphical interface for viewing performance and editing server properties</li>
      <li>Dedicated tools to create and restore server backups</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
